\" data-kid=\"137\">Please authenticate with your clinical registration</p>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"p-3 bg-[#50C878]/10 border border-[#50C878]/25 rounded-xl text-slate-700 text-xs font-body flex items-start gap-2 mb-5\" data-kid=\"138\">\n            <i class=\"ti ti-circle-check text-base text-[#38a15a] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"139\"></i>\n            <div data-kid=\"140\">\n              <span class=\"font-bold text-[#38a15a]\" data-kid=\"141\">Credential Session Active:</span> Verify database integrity after successful sign-in.\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault(); switchTab('chat');\" class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"142\">\n            <div data-kid=\"143\">\n              <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1.5\" data-kid=\"144\">Clinic Email Address</label>\n              <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"145\">\n                <span class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400\" data-kid=\"146\"><i class=\"ti ti-mail text-sm\" data-kid=\"147\"></i></span>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"stella.mercer@klinic.ai\" value=\"kesavardhan775@gmail.com\" class=\"w-full h-10 pl-9 pr-4 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"148\">\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div data-kid=\"149\">\n              <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center mb-1.5\" data-kid=\"150\">\n                <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500\" data-kid=\"151\">Security Password</label>\n                <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-xs text-[#318CE7] hover:underline font-heading font-semibold\" data-kid=\"152\">Forgot Key?</a>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"153\">\n                <span class=\"absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400\" data-kid=\"154\"><i class=\"ti ti-key text-sm\" data-kid=\"155\"></i></span>\n                <input type=\"password\" value=\"Realmegt3t@\" class=\"w-full h-10 pl-9 pr-10 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"156\">\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"absolute right-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-600\" data-kid=\"157\"><i class=\"ti ti-eye text-sm\" data-kid=\"158\"></i></button>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"flex items-center\" data-kid=\"159\">\n              <input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"remember-me\" checked class=\"w-4 h-4 rounded-sm border-white/80 bg-white/50 text-[#318CE7] focus:ring-[#318CE7]/15\" data-kid=\"160\">\n              <label for=\"remember-me\" class=\"ml-2 text-xs text-slate-600 font-body\" data-kid=\"161\">Remember this clinician terminal</label>\n            </div>\n\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full h-11 mt-2 bg-[#318CE7] hover:bg-[#2574c2] text-white rounded-xl text-xs font-heading font-extrabold tracking-wider uppercase transition-all shadow-md shadow-[#318CE7]/20 flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"162\">\n              Sign In to Suite <i class=\"ti ti-arrow-right\" data-kid=\"163\"></i>\n            </button>\n          </form>\n\n          <div class=\"text-center mt-5 text-xs font-body text-slate-500\" data-kid=\"164\">\n            Don't have a secure workspace? <button onclick=\"switchTab('signup')\" class=\"text-[#318CE7] font-semibold hover:underline cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"165\">Request Creation</button>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  \n  <main id=\"screen-signup\" class=\"flex-1 flex overflow-hidden w-full hidden\" data-kid=\"166\">\n    <div class=\"w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center p-12 bg-[#F0F8FF]/30\" data-kid=\"167\">\n      \n      <div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl glass-panel rounded-2xl overflow-hidden flex shadow-2xl border border-white/50\" data-kid=\"168\">\n        \n        \n        <div class=\"w-[55%] p-8 flex flex-col justify-center\" data-kid=\"169\">\n          <div class=\"mb-5\" data-kid=\"170\">\n            <span class=\"text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 block mb-1\" data-kid=\"171\">SUITE PROVISIONING</span>\n            <h3 class=\"font-heading font-extrabold text-xl text-slate-800\" data-kid=\"172\">Establish Clinical Account</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-xs font-body text-slate-500\" data-kid=\"173\">Provide medical credentials to configure workspace</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <form onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault(); switchTab('chat');\" class=\"space-y-3.5\" data-kid=\"174\">\n            <div data-kid=\"175\">\n              <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1\" data-kid=\"176\">Full Name & Clinical Suffix</label>\n              <input type=\"text\" id=\"signup-fullname\" placeholder=\"Dr. Kesavardhan Makireddi\" class=\"w-full h-9 px-3 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"177\">\n            </div>\n\n            <div data-kid=\"178\">\n              <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1\" data-kid=\"179\">Verified Medical License Email</label>\n              <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"k.makireddi775@hospital.org\" class=\"w-full h-9 px-3 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"180\">\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\" data-kid=\"181\">\n              <div data-kid=\"182\">\n                <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1\" data-kid=\"183\">Secure Password</label>\n                <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"184\">\n                  <input type=\"password\" id=\"signup-pass\" oninput=\"validatePassword()\" placeholder=\"••••••••\" class=\"w-full h-9 px-3 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"185\">\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div data-kid=\"186\">\n                <label class=\"block text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 mb-1\" data-kid=\"187\">Confirm Password</label>\n                <div class=\"relative\" data-kid=\"188\">\n                  <input type=\"password\" id=\"signup-confirm-pass\" oninput=\"validatePassword()\" placeholder=\"••••••••\" class=\"w-full h-9 px-3 text-xs font-body rounded-lg bg-white/60 border border-white/80 focus:border-[#318CE7] focus:outline-hidden transition-all text-slate-800\" required data-kid=\"189\">\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            \n            <div class=\"space-y-1.5 pt-1\" data-kid=\"190\">\n              <div class=\"flex justify-between items-center\" data-kid=\"191\">\n                <span class=\"text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400\" data-kid=\"192\">Security Strength Meter</span>\n                <span id=\"strength-label\" class=\"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-slate-400\" data-kid=\"193\">Weak</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"grid grid-cols-4 gap-1.5\" data-kid=\"194\">\n                <div id=\"meter-1\" class=\"h-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all\" data-kid=\"195\"></div>\n                <div id=\"meter-2\" class=\"h-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all\" data-kid=\"196\"></div>\n                <div id=\"meter-3\" class=\"h-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all\" data-kid=\"197\"></div>\n                <div id=\"meter-4\" class=\"h-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all\" data-kid=\"198\"></div>\n              </div>\n              <p id=\"match-label\" class=\"text-xs font-body text-slate-400 font-semibold\" data-kid=\"199\"></p>\n            </div>\n\n            <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full h-10 mt-1 bg-[#318CE7] hover:bg-[#2574c2] text-white rounded-lg text-xs font-heading font-extrabold tracking-wider uppercase transition-all shadow-md flex items-center justify-center gap-1.5 cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"200\">\n              Provision Workspace <i class=\"ti ti-activity-heartbeat\" data-kid=\"201\"></i>\n            </button>\n          </form>\n          \n          <div class=\"text-center mt-3 text-xs font-body text-slate-500\" data-kid=\"202\">\n            Already registered? <button onclick=\"switchTab('signin')\" class=\"text-[#318CE7] font-semibold hover:underline cursor-pointer\" data-kid=\"203\">Sign in directly</button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        \n        <div class=\"w-[45%] bg-[#318CE7]/10 border-l border-white/40 p-8 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden\" data-kid=\"204\">\n          \n          <div class=\"space-y-4\" data-kid=\"205\">\n            <span class=\"px-2.5 py-1 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-md rounded-full text-xs font-heading font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[#318CE7] border border-white/40 inline-block\" data-kid=\"206\">HIPAA & SOC-2 Verified</span>\n            <h4 class=\"font-heading font-extrabold text-lg text-slate-800 leading-tight\" data-kid=\"207\">Advanced clinical tools included</h4>\n            \n            <div class=\"space-y-2.5 text-xs font-body text-slate-600\" data-kid=\"208\">\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\" data-kid=\"209\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-shield-lock text-sm text-[#318CE7] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"210\"></i>\n                <span data-kid=\"211\">Secure patient diagnostic records storage with 256-bit encryption</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\" data-kid=\"212\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-microscope text-sm text-[#50C878] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"213\"></i>\n                <span data-kid=\"214\">Direct PubMed reference linkages on clinical summaries</span>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-2\" data-kid=\"215\">\n                <i class=\"ti ti-brand-zoom text-sm text-[#318CE7] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" data-kid=\"216\"></i>\n                <span data-kid=\"217\">Automated doctor-patient clinical session summarization logs</span>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          \n          <div class=\"relative bg-white/50 rounded-xl p-3 border border-white/60 mt-4\" data-kid=\"218\">\n            <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" data-kid=\"219\">\n              <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559757296-5c84adc6d116?auto=format&w=150&q=80&fit=crop\" alt=\"Clinical AI Graphic\" class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-lg object-cover\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-kid=\"220\">\n              <div data-kid=\"221\">\n                <p class=\"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-slate-800 leading-none\" data-kid=\"222\">Diagnostic Library</p>\n                <p class=\"text-xs font-body text-slate-500 mt-1\" data-kid=\"223\">100K+ clinically certified studies synced hourly</p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n        </div>\n\n      </div>\n\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n</div>\n\n\n<script data-kid=\"224\">\n  // Tab Switching Functionality\n  function switchTab(target) {\n    // Hide all screens\n    document.getElementById('screen-chat').classList.add('hidden');\n    document.getElementById('screen-signin').classList.add('hidden');\n    document.getElementById('screen-signup').classList.add('hidden');\n\n    // Reset tab button states\n    const tabs = ['chat', 'signin', 'signup'];\n    tabs.forEach(t => {\n      const btn = document.getElementById('tab-' + t);\n      if (btn) {\n        btn.className = \"px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-heading font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-1.5 text-slate-600 hover:text-slate-900 cursor-pointer\";\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Show active screen and highlight active button\n    if (target === 'chat') {\n      document.getElementById('screen-chat').classList.remove('hidden');\n      document.getElementById('tab-chat').className = \"px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-heading font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#318CE7] text-white shadow-sm cursor-pointer\";\n    } else if (target === 'signin') {\n      document.getElementById('screen-signin').classList.remove('hidden');\n      document.getElementById('tab-signin').className = \"px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-heading font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#318CE7] text-white shadow-sm cursor-pointer\";\n    } else if (target === 'signup') {\n      document.getElementById('screen-signup').classList.remove('hidden');\n      document.getElementById('tab-signup').className = \"px-5 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs font-heading font-semibold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-[#318CE7] text-white shadow-sm cursor-pointer\";\n    }\n  }\n\n  // Predefined simulated answers mapping\n  const answers = {\n    1: {\n      question: \"What are the symptoms of chronic migraines?\",\n      answer: \"Chronic migraine is officially diagnosed when a patient experiences headaches on at least 15 days per month for more than 3 months, with at least 8 of those days meeting criteria for a migraine. Key symptoms include: moderate-to-severe throbbing physical pain localized to one side of the brain, clinical hypersensitivity to lighting or noise, and intense nauseous symptoms. <br><br><strong>Clinical References:</strong> PubMed Reference ID: PMC6135111; International Headache Society Guidelines (IHS-ICHD-3).\"\n    },\n    2: {\n      question: \"Analyze a heart-healthy diet\",\n      answer: \"A validated cardiovascular clinical diet focuses heavily on dietary fiber, high-quality antioxidant polyphenols, and monounsaturated fatty acids (specifically oleic acids). Key guidelines include restricting saturated trans-fats below 5% of total caloric intake, prioritizing the Mediterranean diet, incorporating olive oil and leafy greens, and managing sodium intake under 1,500mg daily. <br><br><strong>Clinical References:</strong> American Heart Association Diet and Lifestyle Recommendations (AHA 2021 Update); Journal of Clinical Cardiology PMC78241.\"\n    },\n    3: {\n      question: \"How does a stethoscope amplify sound?\",\n      answer: \"A classic acoustic stethoscope relies on direct physical resonance transmission. The shallow, high-tension polymer chestpiece diaphragm acts to collect and concentrate high-frequency clinical chest sounds (like heart valve snaps). This acoustic kinetic wave transfers immediately up hollow soundproof double-tubes to the clinician's ear canal, avoiding loss of frequency amplitude. <br><br><strong>Clinical References:</strong> Littmann Cardiology Acoustic Transmission Manual Section 4; Journal of Medical Engineering & Design.\"\n    }\n  };\n\n  // Simulating the clinical chat flow\n  function simulateQuery(id) {\n    const data = answers[id];\n    if (!data) return;\n\n    // Transition welcome state to chat screen state\n    document.getElementById('welcome-state').classList.add('hidden');\n    document.getElementById('dynamic-chat-history').classList.remove('hidden');\n\n    // Append User message\n    appendMessage(data.question, true);\n\n    // Show typing state\n    const typingIndicator = document.getElementById('bot-typing-indicator');\n    typingIndicator.classList.remove('hidden');\n    scrollChatBottom();\n\n    // Delayed AI response simulation\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      typingIndicator.classList.add('hidden');\n      appendMessage(data.answer, false);\n      scrollChatBottom();\n    }, 1800);\n  }\n\n  // Handle custom manual send action\n  function handleSendText() {\n    const inputElement = document.getElementById('custom-user-input');\n    const text = inputElement.value.trim();\n    if (!text) return;\n\n    document.getElementById('welcome-state').classList.add('hidden');\n    document.getElementById('dynamic-chat-history').classList.remove('hidden');\n\n    // Append User message\n    appendMessage(text, true);\n    inputElement.value = '';\n\n    // Show typing state\n    const typingIndicator = document.getElementById('bot-typing-indicator');\n    typingIndicator.classList.remove('hidden');\n    scrollChatBottom();\n\n    // Delayed default response simulation\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      typingIndicator.classList.add('hidden');\n      const defaultAnswer = `I have received your custom diagnostic prompt: \"${text}\". <br><br>My natural language processing layers are compiling appropriate peer-reviewed clinical research files on this query. If this matches symptoms of a specific condition, please note that clinical evaluation is mandatory. <br><br><strong>Clinical Reference Code:</strong> PubMed Search Query ID: PMC-${Math.floor(100000 + Math.random() * 900000)}.`;\n      appendMessage(defaultAnswer, false);\n      scrollChatBottom();\n    }, 1800);\n  }\n\n  // Append customized chat bubbles\n  function appendMessage(text, isUser) {\n    const historyContainer = document.getElementById('dynamic-chat-history');\n    const messageRow = document.createElement('div');\n    messageRow.className = isUser ? \"flex justify-end items-start gap-3\" : \"flex justify-start items-start gap-3\";\n\n    if (isUser) {\n      messageRow.innerHTML = `\n        <div class=\"p-3.5 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-xs bg-[#318CE7] text-white max-w-[75%] text-sm font-body shadow-xs leading-relaxed\">\n          ${text}\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-slate-300 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm text-slate-700 text-xs font-heading font-bold\">\n          DM\n        </div>\n      `;\n    } else {\n      messageRow.innerHTML = `\n        <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#318CE7] to-[#50C878] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm text-white\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-heartbeat text-sm\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-xs glass-panel max-w-[75%] text-sm font-body text-slate-700 leading-relaxed\">\n          ${text}\n        </div>\n      `;\n    }\n\n    historyContainer.appendChild(messageRow);\n  }\n\n  // Clear chat feed and restore initial welcome state\n  function clearChat() {\n    const historyContainer = document.getElementById('dynamic-chat-history');\n    historyContainer.innerHTML = `\n      <div class=\"flex justify-start items-start gap-3\">\n        <div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#318CE7] to-[#50C878] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-sm text-white\">\n          <i class=\"ti ti-heartbeat text-sm\"></i>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-3.5 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-xs glass-panel max-w-[75%] text-sm font-body text-slate-700 leading-relaxed\">\n          Hello Dr. Mercer, I am ready to process your query. Click any suggestion pill or type customized clinical data below.\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    `;\n    document.getElementById('dynamic-chat-history').classList.add('hidden');\n    document.getElementById('welcome-state').classList.remove('hidden');\n  }\n\n  function scrollChatBottom() {\n    const container = document.getElementById('chat-messages-container');\n    container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;\n  }\n\n  // Interactive password validation meters for Sign Up Screen\n  function validatePassword() {\n    const pass = document.getElementById('signup-pass').value;\n    const confirm = document.getElementById('signup-confirm-pass').value;\n    const label = document.getElementById('strength-label');\n    const matchLabel = document.getElementById('match-label');\n\n    // Simple strength logic\n    let score = 0;\n    if (pass.length > 5) score++;\n    if (pass.length > 8) score++;\n    if (/[A-Z]/.test(pass)) score++;\n    if (/[0-9!@#\\$%\\^&\\*]/.test(pass)) score++;\n\n    // Color code meters\n    const meters = [1, 2, 3, 4];\n    meters.forEach(i => {\n      document.getElementById('meter-' + i).className = \"h-1 bg-slate-200 rounded-full transition-all\";\n    });\n\n    if (score === 1) {\n      document.getElementById('meter-1').className = \"h-1 bg-red-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      label.innerText = \"Weak\";\n      label.className = \"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-red-500\";\n    } else if (score === 2) {\n      document.getElementById('meter-1').className = \"h-1 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-2').className = \"h-1 bg-yellow-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      label.innerText = \"Fair\";\n      label.className = \"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-yellow-500\";\n    } else if (score === 3) {\n      document.getElementById('meter-1').className = \"h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-2').className = \"h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-3').className = \"h-1 bg-blue-400 rounded-full transition-all\";\n      label.innerText = \"Strong\";\n      label.className = \"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-blue-500\";\n    } else if (score >= 4) {\n      document.getElementById('meter-1').className = \"h-1 bg-[#50C878] rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-2').className = \"h-1 bg-[#50C878] rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-3').className = \"h-1 bg-[#50C878] rounded-full transition-all\";\n      document.getElementById('meter-4').className = \"h-1 bg-[#50C878] rounded-full transition-all\";\n      label.innerText = \"Clinical-Grade Secure\";\n      label.className = \"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-[#50C878]\";\n    } else {\n      label.innerText = \"Too short\";\n      label.className = \"text-xs font-heading font-extrabold text-slate-400\";\n    }\n\n    // Passwords Match validation\n    if (confirm) {\n      if (pass === confirm) {\n        matchLabel.innerText = \"✓ Clinical credentials match securely\";\n        matchLabel.className = \"text-xs font-body text-[#50C878] font-semibold\";\n      } else {\n        matchLabel.innerText = \"✗ Security credentials mismatched\";\n        matchLabel.className = \"text-xs font-body text-red-400 font-semibold\";\n      }\n    } else {\n      matchLabel.innerText = \"\";\n    }\n  }\n</script>\n>>>>>>> REPLACE",
